item.title: 10 Surprising Facts About the Amazon Rainforest
item.dc:creator: Ethan Walker, M.Sc.
item.description: Discover the hidden wonders of the Amazon Rainforest! 🌿 From its rich biodiversity to its crucial role in our climate, these surprising facts will change your perspective. Did you know it houses more than 400 billion trees? Dive in to learn more! #AmazonRainforest #NatureFacts #ExploreTheWild 🌍
